Natalie Talmadge https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natalie_Talmadge 0 Natalie Talmadge (April 29, 1896 – June 19, 1969) was an American silent film actress who was best known as the wife of Buster Keaton, and sister of her movie star siblings, Norma and Constance Talmadge. She retired from acting in 1923.
